item.title: [HBASE-11166] Categorize tests in hbase-prefix-tree module
item.description: Jeff Bowles discovered that tests in hbase-prefix-tree module, e.g. TestTimestampEncoder, don't have test category

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.
